{"tid":775133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國女留學生欠租銷聲匿迹　隨處丟避孕套染血內褲　遺留吃剩食物生蛆蟲","createTime":"2018-08-11T01:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T10:56:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b5be947f8fb2862f2328c62cfe2507bc90dd5948","tid":775133,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"韓國一名中國留學生需要回國半年，把房間租給另一名中國女留學生。該留學生在半年間將房間弄得垃圾遍地，甚至有蛆蟲在未收拾的垃圾上面，並拖欠房租不知所終。<br />\n<br />\n原本在首爾租屋的中國留學生，因要回國半年，今年4月初，在網上把房間租給另一名女留學生，並向她收一個月的房租作為按金，和要求她直接向其房東繳交每個月的房租。<br />\n<br />\n在5月左右，出租房間的學生收到該名女留學生的信息，指資金周轉不靈，希望出租者可以退回押金，下個月再還，出租者不虞有詐，退回按金。直至7月時，女留學生突然指她已離開首爾，並直認沒有鎖上大門就搬走。<br />\n<br />\n出租者回到房間後發現，整個房間遍地食物及垃圾，到處都是亂放的被鋪及內衣，更有煙頭及避孕套，更甚的是，有蛆蟲出現在吃剩的食物上。出租者指，不少屋內傢俬都被弄壞，木地板被水浸過而捲起來，百葉窗亦出現破洞。之後她用了一星期打掃，清走10大袋垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n該女生遺留的學生證顯示，她是青島農業大學2016年級商務英語專業的學生，拖欠水電及房租等費用共1.5萬元人民幣。出租者其後嘗試聯絡這名女生時發現，已被封鎖至黑名單，無法再聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180810/s00004/1533883600236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180810%2Fs00004%2F1533883600236&d=QBSkKEYAiAUBAIaFAeT1IAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=18a83c6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180810%2Fs00004%2F1533883600236&h=e6f45803\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180810/s00004/1533883600236</a>"},{"pid":"42bc43a471e6c97bb19f4aa4330ef456dff3b281","tid":775133,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:03:28.000Z","msg":"做雞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4664c1d28de30c1aafdc4518e296bc1b4bb8871","tid":775133,"uid":83251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:03:50.000Z","msg":"借求學為名，做雞為實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d5fb35c95b085dc0581400560fdb8a5bb0ec52","tid":775133,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:05:55.000Z","msg":"&quot;<em>原本在首爾租屋的中國留學生，因要回國半年，今年4月初，在網上把房間租給另一名中國女留學生</em>&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2343e1e0703183f464bafe0cf131a5125355768","tid":775133,"uid":42487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"熱情的臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab8f8bbd0eb59688c9eb3fb512c43be7de9a1f5","tid":775133,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"我諗好難再租俾中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1aa555a9e935b56996e396617722dedaac604d9","tid":775133,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:30:24.000Z","msg":"支蛆"},{"pid":"5940892b2739f7f01a1c4a1729c31cd23248bc0b","tid":775133,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89d5fb35c95b085dc0581400560fdb8a5bb0ec52","tid":775133,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:05:55.000Z","msg":"&quot;<em>原本在首爾租屋的中國留學生，因要回國半年，今年4月初，在網上把房間租給另一名中國女留學生</em>&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"應該得返贏国人信贏国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f9051541b7476866620b6b24c9d06744c88eda","tid":775133,"uid":49588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"中國支蛆並不是浪得虛名！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9606c02a4928595f8ee0a397e3c282a6522657","tid":775133,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2eca03a519647aff8f09e440311f04e5b584c30","tid":775133,"